---
title: Haloumi, Chicken & Caramelised Onion Tacos  with Cucumber Salad & Mayo
description: You thought there couldn’t be any more ways left to enjoy squeaky and salty slices of haloumi. If you did, then we’re going to prove you wrong with haloumi tacos! Pack them up with caramelised onion, chicken bites and a drizzle of mayo and you have yet another haloumi success story.
